high_descs: walk across the kitchen to the coffee machine on the counter next to the sink
take the mug from the machine
walk the mug over to the front of the refridgerator
put the mug in the freezer for a moment then remove
walk the mug back over in front of the coffee machine
place the mug back in it's designated spot where it came from
anns.task_desc: get the mug from the coffee machine, put it in the freezer, then put it back on the machine

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the coffee maker to the right of the sink.
Take the mug out of the coffee maker.
Walk right to the fridge.
Place the mug in the fridge and close the door. Wait a moment and take it out again.
Step left back to the coffee maker.
Place the mug back in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug in a coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to the coffee machine near the toaster.
Pick up the mug which is on the coffee machine.
Turn right and walk to the refrigerator.
Put the mug in the refrigerator for a few seconds, then take it out and close the refrigerator.
Turn left and walk back to the coffee machine.
Put the mug back on the coffee machine, in its original position.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled mug on a coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn walk, walk straight and hang left to go to the coffee maker.
Pick up the mug out of the coffee maker.
Take a step right to the fridge.
Put the mug on the top left shelf and close the door. After a moment, take the mug out of the fridge.
Take a step to the left.
Return the mug its original position in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug in a coffee maker.

high_descs: turn to the right and make a left into kitchen
go forward to coffee machine and pick mug
turn to right and go to refrigerator
open refrigerator, place mug inside, then close it. open refrigerator, take out mug.
go to the left, then place mug in coffee machine.
leave mug in coffee machine
anns.task_desc: make mug cold before making coffee

high_descs: Turn right and walk so you are slightly to the right of the sink facing a coffee maker.
Pick up the mug off of it's spot under the coffee maker.
Turn right and position yourself in front of the fridge facing it.
Open the fridge and put the mug on the fourth cubby to the left and close the fridge letting the mug chill for a while before retrieving it and closing the fridge again.
Turn left and move back in front of the coffee maker.
Place the mug in it's place under the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug under the coffee maker.
